pages.title: Inland Taipan
pages.text: The species is endemic to semi-arid regions of central east Australia.$(br2)Aboriginal Australians living in those regions named the snake dandarabilla.$(br2)The inland taipan is a specialist hunter of mammals, so its venom is specially adapted to kill warm-blooded species.
